  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>Yes</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In patients under general anesthesia the investigators wish to investigate association and
      covariance between a peripheral perfusion index as obtained by Radical 7 monitor (Masimo,
      Irvine, CA, USA) and more traditional hemodynamic parameters, ie. invasive blood pressure
      and SV as obtained by LiDCO rapid monitor (LiDCO Ldt., London, UK)
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
